txt.en: You have found a sparkling rune-stone
You have found a chiselled rune-stone
You have found an ancient rune-stone
Even in the darkest deeps, this rock glints like moonlight on a many-faceted gemstone.
This stone has been carefully shaped and crafted by the end of a pick to reflect the thought of its maker.
Find hidden rune-stones in the Dark Delvings
You have found a dim rune-stone
This rune-stone is so old that its weathered surface is as soft and smooth as silk cloth.
The dim rune-stone is unremarkable in every way, faded and dark, and almost seems as though it wishes to remain lost in Dark Delvings.
